Frank B. Hall and Co, aninsurance and brokerage firm, said it has joined with &lt;RiskScience International> to offer banks a new service thatassesses their environmental risk level.    Hall said that under recently enacted legislation banks andother financial institutions can be held liable forenvironmental risks in projects that they finance.    Therefore, Hall said, RSI will evaluate a property, assignit an environmental risk level and advise the bank about itsoptions to reduce environmental risks. Reuter&#3;